"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Today, we‚Äôre excited to announce Metalink now supports **Multiple Wallets**.\\n\\nYou can now attach more than one wallet to your account and verify your holdings on each one.\\n\\n## 3 Reasons Why This Is A Big Deal\\n\\n### #1) Access All Your Channels From One Account\\n\\nYou no longer need to transfer your NFTs into one wallet or create multiple Metalink accounts in order to access your collection channels.\\n\\n### #2) Safer For Hardware Wallets\\n\\n**81% of hacks happen because passwords are compromised.** With a ‚Äúno password‚Äù log-in, Metalink is positioned to be a safe and secure platform.\\n\\nHowever, it can still be scary at times to log-in to any web3 platform with your hardware wallet. If you use Ledger, you will no longer need to log-in multiple times with it.\\n\\nInstead, you can log-in ONCE with your Ledger, and add a secondary Metamask wallet to your account for daily use. This could even be a blank wallet. Moving forward, you can use this hot wallet to sign in and out.\\n\\n### #3) Track All Your Holdings In My Collection.\\n\\nMy Collection has become one of the most used portfolio trackers for NFT collectors. Now you can track your holdings across multiple wallets to get the full picture of your collection‚Äôs value.\\n\\n## How To Use Multiple Wallets\\n\\n### 1) Login with your first wallet and head to your Profile Settings.\\n\\n![Settings page on Metalink](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/yoK_tWvEzHpxw317470iT.jpeg?height=1176&width=2054)\\n\\n### 2) Click ‚ÄòConnect Wallet‚Äô to add an additional wallet.\\n\\n![Sorry for the ugly design. Since so many of you asked for it, we focused more on utility and will be updating design later.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/MZIDp4C5UAvP-_DcngUtP.jpeg?height=1708&width=2950)\\n\\n### 3) And you‚Äôre all set!\\n\\n![Voila! üé©](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/am1DjNKzDvsUvJKlhLJd-.jpeg?height=1252&width=2192)\\n\\n## From the entire team at Metalink, we want to wish you a Merry Christmas (Eve) and Happy Holidays!\\n\\nRegardless of your beliefs, the holidays is a great time to pause and reflect on where we‚Äôve been been and where we‚Äôre going next. *Wen moon?*\\n\\nHope you have a safe and amazing day and look forward to ringing in the new year with you next week!\\n\\nLastly, make sure you‚Äôre on NFT twitter this Sunday‚Ä¶ There‚Äôs something coming that you might not want to miss‚Ä¶ ü§ë üê£\",\"timestamp\":1640497956,\"title\":\"üéÅüéÑ Day 9 of 12 Days of Metalink - Multiple Wallets üéÅüéÑ\"},\"digest\":\"ApCUiJC_vp0was6b6pejfjCSfSOl5kCDKyc6h27dlmI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xa5331E8929b83E66E15b4F199f5cD78aE61C60f3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PKjyBDgcwdU5eO9VNTFO0KoUeSPLFbaAQNJcNoNA5bM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IM0lq1kI5OEQcc82v2Zbu5nXL5Z5cHYV6qCHLywzVAk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"toOO18Q9wvBhF4fgngpE7nAWY7G4ckXurw4Fkx9NPuxk3CdS8u6IvPlr28tOHn1nNHqBJ-1wQNLReas8VYZW8Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8d43a80f0074a28d3aca7c48bb5232e39f932750bdf0685677bd8bc28bc69f5e645252dcb2867e1a7e7256b0209a60014f6f6e1cd65bd1a11e47277ae549e8051b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PKjyBDgcwdU5eO9VNTFO0KoUeSPLFbaAQNJcNoNA5bM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IM0lq1kI5OEQcc82v2Zbu5nXL5Z5cHYV6qCHLywzVAk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"saXnLkLGTwFfbAOysfFEM8cENcc4Qbp5ueRKWTImhpk\"}"